name: Proibido (No. 2)
description: This work is part of a series named "Worthless Gurskys", devoted to large scale and minimalist urban visual scenes. Inscription on the weathered varnish of a wooden dor, somewhere in São Paulo city, February 4th 2012. Remastered from the original raw file in 2021. Originally released as HeN OBJKT 101005 on 27 May 2021.
